#Adjust titles, labels, and limits
sns.swarmplot(x="day", y="total_bill", data=tips);
plt.title("Distribution of Bill Amount ($)") #Add plot title
plt.ylabel("Total Bill ($)") #Adjust the label of the y-axis
plt.xlabel("Day of week") #Adjust the label of the x-axis
plt.ylim(0,100) #Adjust the limits of the y-axis
